title: Evacuees wait to fill gas tanks at Quik Stop on Hwy 99 and Bogue Road
text: Evacuees wait to fill gas tanks at Quik Stop on Hwy 99 and Bogue Road Feb 12, 2017 An evacuation order prompted by the erosion of the emergency spillway at Oroville Dam produced lines of vehicles on Bogue Road at Highway 99, coming out of Yuba City.
